high_descs: Move three steps to your left so you are looking at the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the loaf of bread that's on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the bread on the first shelf in the middle then close the fridge and let it cool before you open the fridge retrieve the bread and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is on the counter to the right of the coffee maker.
Turn around with the loaf of bread and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Put the loaf of bread on the second shelf and close the fridge door.  Open the fridge and grab the loaf of bread on the second shelf.
Turn to your left with the loaf of bread.  Go to the sink.
Place the loaf of bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take loaf of bread to counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the end of the counter near the coffee maker.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door. Place the loaf on the second shelf. Close the refrigerator door for seven seconds. Open the fridge door and take out the loaf. Close the fridge door.
Turn left and take the loaf over to the sink.
Place the bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread in the refrigerator for seven seconds, put it on the counter next to the sink.
